creator: Opus Lounge
descriptionHtml:
Buccaneer Sessions is a new community app designed for action and adventure sports, utilising the latest in mobile technology to connect locations, sports and activities with those who enjoy them.

Join our collective - find new spots, create and join sessions, get messages, news and session alerts from locations, local businesses, pros or friends. Never miss an opportunity to get out there and do the things you love. Learn more at: buccaneersessions.com

Buccaneer has been set up and is run by genuine action sports participants.

The concept is to deliver a location based, community network specifically aimed at action sports, connecting the places and locations (beaches, breaks, trails, hills, mountains and crags) with the people that use and enjoy them.

We want our users to be able to share group messaging, events, access to pros, skill clinics, retail and equipment, pictures, video and stories of our adventures.

Features Include:

- Cool location guide - All the information you need to know about what is happening and where.

- Easy GPS link to locate a difficult to find spots.

- Feel free to join our collective and update location data and we will credit you by name. Help make the app more useful!!

- Sessions Platform: Record your activated and share tales of your adventures. Create and attend Sessions at locations, See what’s happening where and when.

-Access to contact details for local amenities, gear shops, refreshment, training centres and Pro's.

- Link to and follow your favourite Pro’s

- Favourite the locations you want to stay connected to.

- Receive an automated feed of services and news from your favourited locations and service providers.

- Connect to the pros, instructors and schools you want to follow.

- Easy credit card booking and payment mechanism for classes, courses or skill clinics

Buccaneer Location Data

Buccaneer has mapped hundreds of locations already. We would really like location data to add as much value to our community as possible, so we want to encourage you to send us updates. Some of our locations have been populated already some are awaiting input.

Bear with us while to build our data and feel free to get stuck in. We will credit any user that send us an update.

Pro’s and Local Businesses

Buccaneer Sessions features a business profiles enabling you to connect directly to your existing clients and new ones! The app brings together multi disciplines and sports so will widen the scope and accessibility for new participants to every sport and activity featured.

The application enables you to advertise events and sessions with an easy to use booking and payment platform.

Features Include:

- Link directly to your clients in real time

- Users that follow you or the locations you are listed against will receive an alert and notifications of your activities.

- Easily communicate and promote your services

- Paid sessions platform: Create and advertise paid sessions at locations, see what’s happening where and when

- Payment gate way for clients to book on to sessions, clinic’s and courses

- Easy credit card payment whilst booking

- Get paid easily

- List against your working locations and then any potential clients can see the services you offer.

- Potential clients will automatically get push-notifications of services / activities you want to promote for locations they have favourited
descriptionShort: Connecting you to the amazing locations we kite, surf, sail and ride

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This version introduces a more comprehensive notification system
